他现任穆巴达拉发展公司的董事长。该公司2002年成立，是阿布扎比政府的主要投资工具。穆巴达拉的目标是通过经济多元化和全球投资, 为阿联酋创造长期的社会及经济效益。<ref name="#4">{{Cite web|title=His Highness Sheikh Mohammed Bin Zayed Al Nahyan {{!}} Middle East Alliance Legal Consultancy|url=https://melf.ae/his-highness-sheikh-mohammed-bin-zayed-al-nahyan/|accessdate=2019-08-20|language=en-GB|archive-date=2019-07-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190705043414/https://melf.ae/his-highness-sheikh-mohammed-bin-zayed-al-nahyan/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.ecouncil.ae/en/ADGovernment/Pages/CrownPrince.aspx|accessdate=2019-08-20|work=www.ecouncil.ae|title=存档副本|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190705043415/https://www.ecouncil.ae/en/ADGovernment/Pages/CrownPrince.aspx|archive-date=2019-07-05|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Mubadala Investment Company|url=https://www.mubadala.com/en/home|accessdate=2019-08-20|date=2017-04-03|work=www.mubadala.com|language=en|archive-date=2019-10-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191008231653/https://www.mubadala.com/en/home|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

他还担任该国主要经济规划机构——阿布扎比经济发展委员会（ADCED）的负责人,  以这一身份发起了沙拉卡倡议，旨在改善阿联酋私营部门，简化阿布扎比的业务和投资流程,  带领ADCED采取诸多举措强化阿联酋的企业精神。<ref name="#4"/><ref>{{Cite web|title=Sharaka platform linked to Abu Dhabi government’s TAMM|url=http://www.technicalreviewmiddleeast.com/business-a-management/business-a-management/sharaka-platform-linked-to-abu-dhabi-government-s-tamm|accessdate=2019-08-20|last=Patnaik|first=Rhonita|work=Technical Review Middle East|language=pl|archive-date=2019-05-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190507200258/http://www.technicalreviewmiddleeast.com/business-a-management/business-a-management/sharaka-platform-linked-to-abu-dhabi-government-s-tamm|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2018年6月，他批准了一项为期3年、总计500亿迪拉姆的经济刺激计划，希望为阿联酋及投资者提供长期经济效益。与此同时，他还委托对建筑法规进行全面审查，支持城市发展。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Sheikh Mohammed bin Zayed announces Dh50 billion stimulus for Abu Dhabi|url=https://www.thenational.ae/uae/sheikh-mohammed-bin-zayed-announces-dh50-billion-stimulus-for-abu-dhabi-1.737334|accessdate=2019-08-20|work=The National|language=en|archive-date=2019-06-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190605184543/https://www.thenational.ae/uae/sheikh-mohammed-bin-zayed-announces-dh50-billion-stimulus-for-abu-dhabi-1.737334|dead-url=no}}</ref>

他目前担任阿布扎比投资局（ADI）的副主席；该机构代表阿布扎比人民进行投资，促进经济的多元化和全球化。阿布扎比投资局的投资目标包括二十多个资产类别及子类别。<ref>{{Cite web|title=ADIA|url=https://www.adia.ae/|accessdate=2019-08-20|author=|date=|format=|work=www.adia.ae|publisher=|language=|archive-date=2019-06-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190626160555/https://www.adia.ae/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

